These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: hip-hop, country
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk
1. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | country | hip-hop |
| Beverage     | soy-milk    | mirinda   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: zombie, superhero
City: marseilles, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | zombie        |
| City      | marseilles  | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil
1. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | fanta    | lemonade |
| Flower   | poppy | daffodil |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, spanish
City: miami, marseilles
1. the spanish is on the right of the mexican##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Nationality   | mexican      | spanish |
