.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, july
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, journalist
1. the electrician is in an even position##4
2. the journalist is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Birthday       | july | february  |
| Job   | journalist  | electrician |

 #################################

 
