There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Hobby   | dancing | magic-tricks   |
| Beverage         | almond-milk | cola |

