2 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog
1. the owner of the rat is the person playing poker##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Game   | snooker       | poker   |
| Pet   | hedgehog | rat |

